  "summary": "Apache Wicket has a Session Fixation issue",
  "details": "Missing invocation of Servlet http web request method changeSessionId after session binding can be exploited for a\u00a0session fixation attack in Apache Wicket.\n\nThis issue affects Apache Wicket: from 8.0.0 through 8.17.0, 9.0.0, from 10.0.0 through 10.8.0.\n\nUsers are recommended to upgrade to version 10.9.0, which fixes the issue.",
